00:36:40,280 --> 00:36:41,120
Lu Chang!

573
00:36:43,030 --> 00:36:45,280
Lu Chang, you're selfish.

574
00:36:45,510 --> 00:36:46,840
You knew how heartbroken she'd be

575
00:36:46,840 --> 00:36:47,920
when she learned her identity.

576
00:36:47,960 --> 00:36:48,920
Calm down.

577
00:36:49,710 --> 00:36:50,630
I haven't asked you yet.

578
00:36:51,190 --> 00:36:52,320
Did you tell her?

579
00:36:52,590 --> 00:36:53,430
How could I?

580
00:36:53,710 --> 00:36:55,590
Would I dig my grave to give you a chance?

581
00:36:56,230 --> 00:36:57,550
Arguing won't change anything now.

582
00:36:58,670 --> 00:36:59,630
This is your fault!

583
00:36:59,960 --> 00:37:00,880
As her brother,

584
00:37:01,440 --> 00:37:03,150
you didn't know what was on her mind.

585
00:37:03,920 --> 00:37:05,110
This is indeed my fault,

586
00:37:05,510 --> 00:37:06,350
but...

587
00:37:06,800 --> 00:37:07,640
Qingzhao.

588
00:37:12,760 --> 00:37:13,600
You're here.

589
00:37:13,880 --> 00:37:14,720
Yes, Mingshu.

590
00:37:15,630 --> 00:37:17,480
What are you doing?

591
00:37:19,510 --> 00:37:21,070
Your brother is preparing breakfast for you.

592
00:37:21,320 --> 00:37:22,160
Sit and eat something.

593
00:37:23,190 --> 00:37:24,150
Eat a little.

594
00:37:25,110 --> 00:37:26,280
Your favorite rice cakes.

595
00:37:37,320 --> 00:37:38,160
Mingshu,

596
00:37:38,510 --> 00:37:39,920
I brought your favorite ring cakes.

597
00:37:40,110 --> 00:37:41,400
Do you have an appetite?

598
00:37:42,110 --> 00:37:43,000
Thank you, Qingzhao,

599
00:37:43,760 --> 00:37:44,600
but I have no appetite.

600
00:37:46,960 --> 00:37:47,800
Mingshu,

601
00:37:48,440 --> 00:37:49,590
since you left,

602
00:37:49,880 --> 00:37:50,880
I haven't eaten properly.

603
00:37:52,000 --> 00:37:52,840
Look,

604
00:37:52,840 --> 00:37:53,920
I've lost weight from hunger.

605
00:37:54,920 --> 00:37:56,400
I traveled all night

606
00:37:56,670 --> 00:37:57,710
and I'm starving now.

607
00:37:58,280 --> 00:37:59,120
If you don't eat,

608
00:37:59,360 --> 00:38:00,200
I won't either.

609
00:38:02,320 --> 00:38:03,670
Just eat a little with me.

610
00:38:17,510 --> 00:38:18,480
Stay with her.

611
00:38:19,360 --> 00:38:21,150
I'll go find more of her favorite foods.

612
00:38:30,150 --> 00:38:31,630
Mingshu, have some more.

613
00:38:36,760 --> 00:38:37,600
Why is he here?

614
00:38:40,670 --> 00:38:41,550
He came with Prince Rui

615
00:38:42,230 --> 00:38:43,360
to Jianglin for the investigation.

616
00:38:44,190 --> 00:38:45,440
He couldn't wait to see Mingshu,

617
00:38:46,670 --> 00:38:48,110
so he rode here overnight.

618
00:38:49,320 --> 00:38:50,160
Look at you.

619
00:38:50,590 --> 00:38:52,070
You suffered so much to save her

620
00:38:52,230 --> 00:38:53,320
and even got hurt.

621
00:38:53,510 --> 00:38:54,480
Finally, you're free

622
00:38:54,480 --> 00:38:55,630
from the sibling bond.

623
00:38:55,960 --> 00:38:57,000
Now at this critical moment,

624
00:38:57,400 --> 00:38:58,440
you step aside for someone else.

625
00:38:59,110 --> 00:39:00,280
I really don't get you.

626
00:39:00,800 --> 00:39:02,110
Mingshu just learned about her origins.

627
00:39:02,960 --> 00:39:03,880
She is in a bad mood.

628
00:39:05,880 --> 00:39:06,960
Can't you see it?

629
00:39:07,880 --> 00:39:09,440
Qingzhao comforts her better than I can.

630
00:39:10,630 --> 00:39:11,490
- But...
- Enough.

631
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:13,920
This isn't the time for jealousy.

632
00:39:15,110 --> 00:39:16,760
What matters is helping Mingshu recover.

633
00:39:28,500 --> 00:39:33,500
(Tomb of Master Jian Jinhai, Jianglin)

634
00:39:33,500 --> 00:39:34,740
(Tomb of Fugui)

635
00:39:34,740 --> 00:39:36,340
(Tomb of Xiao Qingting)

636
00:39:38,860 --> 00:39:43,700
(Tomb of Master Jian Jinhai, Jianglin)

637
00:39:43,710 --> 00:39:44,710
Here we are.

638
00:39:46,070 --> 00:39:47,280
After the Jian Family fell,

639
00:39:47,700 --> 00:39:49,280
they couldn't enter their ancestral graveyard

640
00:39:50,150 --> 00:39:51,190
due to their alleged bandit ties.

641
00:39:52,190 --> 00:39:53,030
Uncle Feng,

642
00:39:55,360 --> 00:39:57,030
Ying Xun's father,

643
00:39:57,760 --> 00:39:59,150
had their bodies collected

644
00:40:00,590 --> 00:40:01,630
and buried here.

645
00:40:08,320 --> 00:40:09,320
Jian Jinhai

646
00:40:09,340 --> 00:40:12,540
(Tomb of Master Jian Jinhai, Jianglin)

647
00:40:13,550 --> 00:40:14,800
was your father.

648
00:40:15,920 --> 00:40:17,480
He was charitable.

649
00:40:18,360 --> 00:40:20,630
He founded Jian's Academy,

650
00:40:20,920 --> 00:40:23,360
providing financial aid to many commoners.

651
00:40:24,710 --> 00:40:26,960
I benefited greatly myself.

652
00:40:29,360 --> 00:40:30,360
His devotion to you

653
00:40:31,150 --> 00:40:32,710
was well-known in Jianglin.

654
00:40:33,320 --> 00:40:35,760
He made you the manager of Jian's Gold Shop.

655
00:40:37,710 --> 00:40:38,880
So, in Jianglin,

656
00:40:40,030 --> 00:40:41,360
you were the famous female manager.

657
00:40:49,400 --> 00:40:50,240
Then...

658
00:40:50,800 --> 00:40:51,640
My mother...

659
00:40:52,280 --> 00:40:53,440
Why didn't I see her tomb?

660
00:40:55,280 --> 00:40:56,550
Your mother passed early

661
00:40:57,510 --> 00:40:59,150
and was buried in the ancestral graveyard.

662
00:41:00,550 --> 00:41:01,550
She was very kind too.

663
00:41:05,110 --> 00:41:06,670
When my mother and I arrived in Jianglin,

664
00:41:07,190 --> 00:41:08,230
we were penniless

665
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:10,110
and homeless.

666
00:41:10,630 --> 00:41:11,880
She hired my mother

667
00:41:12,670 --> 00:41:15,110
as an embroideress out of generosity.

668
00:41:16,070 --> 00:41:17,710
That's how we secured shelter.

669
00:41:20,030 --> 00:41:22,920
Our families were connected this way.

670
00:41:24,070 --> 00:41:25,440
So,

671
00:41:25,960 --> 00:41:27,670
we were kind of childhood friends.

672
00:41:29,590 --> 00:41:30,430
That's right.

673
00:41:34,280 --> 00:41:35,120
The one behind

674
00:41:35,360 --> 00:41:37,020
(Tomb of Liu Shun)
is the steward.

675
00:41:37,840 --> 00:41:39,230
He served your family for over a decade.

676
00:41:43,590 --> 00:41:44,430
That's your maid,

677
00:41:45,360 --> 00:41:47,360
(Tomb of Xiao Qingting)
Xiao Qingting.

678
00:41:48,400 --> 00:41:49,280
You used to take her

679
00:41:49,840 --> 00:41:50,680
wherever you went.

680
00:42:02,320 --> 00:42:03,710
These buried underground

681
00:42:05,000 --> 00:42:06,800
