682
00:42:07,800 --> 00:42:10,400
I ought to feel devastated.

683
00:42:11,670 --> 00:42:12,630
Why...

684
00:42:15,000 --> 00:42:17,400
Why can't I remember their voices?

685
00:42:18,030 --> 00:42:20,070
Why can't I recall their faces?

686
00:42:22,000 --> 00:42:24,550
I can't remember anything.

687
00:42:24,550 --> 00:42:25,550
I...

688
00:42:25,550 --> 00:42:26,630
Don't blame yourself.

689
00:42:27,960 --> 00:42:29,150
This isn't your fault.

690
00:42:33,070 --> 00:42:33,910
They

691
00:42:34,880 --> 00:42:35,800
would never blame you.

692
00:42:37,320 --> 00:42:38,280
Your family would only

693
00:42:39,760 --> 00:42:42,110
want you to live a good life.

694
00:43:10,990 --> 00:43:13,540
♪May heaven and earth show mercy♪

695
00:43:13,540 --> 00:43:16,080
♪Let mortal ties never fade♪

696
00:43:17,310 --> 00:43:19,960
♪As time quietly slips away♪

697
00:43:19,960 --> 00:43:23,040
♪Don't let us miss growing old together♪

698
00:43:23,810 --> 00:43:26,290
♪May this heart stay true as the first day♪

699
00:43:26,290 --> 00:43:29,570
♪I'll wait through blooms and dew♪

700
00:43:30,240 --> 00:43:35,120
♪Let greed and wrath fade with the wind♪

701
00:43:36,290 --> 00:43:38,720
♪May life's towers stand tall♪

702
00:43:38,720 --> 00:43:41,210
♪With love that outlasts all♪

703
00:43:42,620 --> 00:43:45,160
♪Together we'll traverse♪

704
00:43:45,160 --> 00:43:48,340
♪Through grandeur and adversity♪

705
00:43:49,100 --> 00:43:51,560
♪When clarity arrives♪

706
00:43:51,560 --> 00:43:54,970
♪Destiny's threads entwine,
Karma's path refines♪

707
00:43:55,560 --> 00:44:00,760
♪In glances back, our story's told♪

708
00:44:01,310 --> 00:44:04,660
♪If all scenes fade to view♪

709
00:44:04,660 --> 00:44:07,590
♪Will you return♪

710
00:44:07,920 --> 00:44:10,680
♪Through years with sincere love♪

711
00:44:10,680 --> 00:44:13,840
♪May all enigmas grow clear♪

712
00:44:14,120 --> 00:44:17,410
♪Counting endless nights♪

713
00:44:17,410 --> 00:44:19,540
♪Yet never your♪

714
00:44:19,540 --> 00:44:25,630
♪Silhouette in sight♪

715
00:44:27,090 --> 00:44:30,060
♪If the moon above the sea is full♪

716
00:44:30,350 --> 00:44:33,140
♪Will you return♪

717
00:44:33,520 --> 00:44:36,440
♪In years left, wait for me♪

718
00:44:36,600 --> 00:44:39,540
♪With a beginning and an end♪

719
00:44:39,810 --> 00:44:42,840
♪May time inscribe our names♪

